@baseUrl=http://127.0.0.1:5000

### /items Get all items
GET {{baseUrl}}/items

### /items Add a new item
POST {{baseUrl}}/items
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "apple",
    "price": 1
}

### /items/<id> Get a specific item
GET {{baseUrl}}/items/123

### /items/<id> Update an item
PUT {{baseUrl}}/items/123
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "red apple",
    "price": 0.8,
    "description": "on sale"
}

### /items/<id> Delete an item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/items/123